(47581, 118740, 0, 5, 'The Love Is On Its Way In the Orange Taiwan Strait', '一首屬於西子灣和高雄港的情歌。\n*原詩來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\n', '2012-05-11 00:00:00', 2012, 0, 2, 5, 'The Love Is on Its Way in the Orange Taiwan Strait\n詞 演唱  大國Gordon Tseng   作曲編曲  Bob Tone \n\nWhat excites the lazy clouds?\nWhat seals the lady’s mouth\nSo it can’t be said aloud?\nOh, what are these all about?\n\nThe ships are on their sunny way\nFrom the harbor’s busy gate.\nHer mind is sailing away\nFor his song in in Xizi Bay.\n\nWhat keeps the whole city far?\nWhat lights up that evening star \nAnd something in his heart?\nOh, what makes the story start?\n\nThe love is on its shiny way \nIn the orange Taiwan Strait.\nHis life is sailing away\nFor her smile in Xizi Bay.\n\n（原詩來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA）\n', '', 250, '', 'Bob Tone', '大國Gordon Tseng', '四行倉庫', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-11 18:43:12', '2015-03-12 13:52:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47582, 118740, 4511, 5, 'Biological Gene', '這首歌反映人類關係中的男女關係（生物版）\r\n－從生物基因的觀點看人間男女的愛情\r\n\r\n來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集 GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n兩首詩：\r\nFrom Her View\r\nFrom His View\r\n＊\r\nFrom Her View\r\n\r\n＊\r\nShe likes his shirt and jeans, \r\nAnd what those flowers mean.\r\nBut, if the time has not yet been,\r\nHer signal will never be green.\r\n\r\n＊\r\n＊\r\nFrom His View\r\n＊\r\nShe might own everything and be perfect like a queen.\r\nBut still, he has to follow the imposed biological gene.\r\nWhether his bridge gets hard enough will critically mean\r\nWhether romance would start and any action be seen.\r\n＊\r\n＊\r\n-from GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n\r\n倉庫字典：\r\nImposed biological gene 被強加的生物基因\r\n\r\n為了調整長度，歌詞稍有修改。\r\n\r\n', '2012-06-08 00:00:00', 2012, 20, 0, 7, 'Biological Gene　　　詞 演唱　 大國Gordon Tseng　作曲編曲　Bob Tone     \r\n*\r\nShe likes his shirt and jeans, \r\nAnd what those fresh flowers mean.\r\nBut, if the time has not yet been,\r\nHer signal will never be green.\r\n\r\nShe might own everything and be perfect like a princess or queen.\r\nBut still, he has to follow the imposed biological gene.\r\nWhether his bridge gets hard enough will definitely critically mean\r\nWhether their romance would gently start and his first action be seen.\r\n*\r\n(來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集 GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA)\r\n', '', 252, '', 'Bob Tone', '大國Gordon Tseng', '四行倉庫', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-11 19:27:43', '2015-03-12 13:52:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47583, 116179, 0, 1, '在遙遠的另一端嗎', '', '2012-05-11 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 5, '生活在大城市裡走走停停\n經過身旁的人也是毫不客氣\n下了好幾天的雨 也成了陸上的魚\n日子在沒有忘記的時候過去\n片段也只能匆忙的留下痕跡\n有點熟悉的旋律 牽引著塵封記憶\n快讓悲傷的情感離去 絕對不能夠放棄\n沒有任何人能夠停下來等你\n樂於在擁擠的人潮中穿梭遊走\n親愛的過客們也不會在乎過客了吧\n為魚總是要往著溫暖的南方游去\n是在遙遠的另一端嗎嗎啊吧\n於是冬天就要這麼過了\n是有那麼一點捨不得啊', '', 292, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-11 19:42:15', '2015-03-12 13:52:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47584, 118740, 4511, 6, 'Their Mr. and Miss Right', '一首帶點cynical and ironical(犬儒與反諷)色彩的都會藍調社會寫真歌曲，不妨聽聽看，如有雷同，笑笑就好。\r\n＊\r\n來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文詩集GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n兩首詩：\r\nHer Mr. Right Is Always Ahead\r\n (她的Mr. Right 永遠在前方)\r\nThe Woman He’d like to Date\r\n(關於他想要約會的女人)\r\n\r\n\r\n', '2012-06-08 00:00:00', 2012, 20, 0, 15, 'Their Mr. and Miss Right \r\n*\r\n詞　大國Gordon Tseng 　曲　Gordon Tseng & Bob Tone 　編曲　Bob Tone　    演唱  大國\r\n*\r\nShe believed what she had read,\r\nHer Mr. Right is always ahead.\r\nShe believed what is said,\r\nThe roses out there are always red.\r\n*\r\nWhen she was 20, lying on her pinky bed, she dreamed about a nice-looking head.\r\nWhen she was 30, she longed for a man with a potential career to let her future be fed.\r\nTurning 40, she still thought she deserved a guy with a decent title or tons of bread.\r\nNow, she’s passed 50 and only asks for a mate who won’t soon be deaf, or dead.\r\n*\r\nShe believed what she had read,\r\nHer Mr. Right is always ahead.\r\nShe believed what is said,\r\nThe roses out there are always red.\r\n*\r\n(間奏)\r\n*\r\nFor him, love is never too late.\r\nIt’s easy to find a woman he’d like to date.\r\nFor him, love is the mission and fate.\r\nIt’s easy to find someone he’d like to wait.\r\n*\r\nWhen he was a boy, he dreamed about a rosy face adorably dressed by beautiful lace.\r\nWhen he was 30, he longed for a passionate lover who can fall in love at a faster pace.\r\nTurning 40, he preferred a lady knowing the difference between grimness and grace.\r\nNow, he has passed 50, all he asks for is an exciting body and a few pills just in case.\r\n*\r\nFor him, love is never too late.\r\nIt’s easy to find a woman he’d like to date.\r\nFor him, love is the mission and fate.\r\nIt’s easy to find someone he’d like to wait.\r\n*\r\nFor him, love is never too late.\r\nFor him, love is the mission and fate.\r\nHer Mr. Right is always ahead.\r\nThe roses out there are always red.\r\n*\r\n\r\n（來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文詩集）\r\n-　from GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n', '', 323, '', '大國Gordon Tseng, Bob Tone', '大國Gordon Tseng', '四行倉庫', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-11 20:16:45', '2015-03-12 13:52:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
