(47587, 118740, 4511, 4, 'From Yes I Do to No We Don''t', '如果你已離婚 你聽了會很想起舞\r\n如果你還沒離婚 你聽了會很知足\r\n如果你還沒結婚 你聽了會變成熟\r\n＊\r\n來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集 GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n兩首詩：\r\nYes, I Do \r\nNo, We Don’t　\r\n\r\n　', '2012-06-08 00:00:00', 2012, 20, 0, 1, 'From Yes, I Do to No, We Don’t　　\r\n詞　大國Gordon Tseng　作曲編曲　Bob Tone     演唱　大國\r\n＊\r\nHis words need a love boat to ferry.\r\nHer face looks rosy, oh, very, very.\r\nTheir tale has so many promises to carry\r\nFor the right one they are ready to marry.  \r\n＊\r\n(So, do they live happily hereafter?)\r\n＊\r\nHis words become so airy.\r\nHer face looks very scary.\r\nTheir tale is nothing fairy\r\nAnd ready for an agreement to bury.\r\n＊\r\n(Yes, I do!)\r\n(No, we don’t!)\r\n＊\r\n(So, will they expect happiness again?)\r\n\r\n\r\n（來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集）\r\n-　from GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n', '', 300, '', 'Bob Tone', '大國Gordon Tseng', '四行倉庫', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-11 20:49:40', '2015-03-12 13:52:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(47588, 118740, 4511, 2, 'Still, How Many', '這首歌反映強勢文明與弱勢文明的關係（戰爭版）\r\n*\r\n來自大國Gordon Tseng的英文四行詩集GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n\r\n\r\nStill, How Many \r\n*\r\n\r\nHow many lands will get showers of bullets made of new alloy?\r\n\r\nHow many creatures would perish after the jetfighters’ cool ‘hoy’?\r\n\r\nHow many wars does a nation have to win to own real peaceful joy?\r\n\r\nThe answer has been there since they tried to educate the foreign red boy.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n- from GOD BLESS NOT ONLY AMERICA\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n這首大國Gordon Tseng詩集中的英文四行詩原是針對美國人寫的，red boy指印第安男孩。在寫成歌曲時，為了更能反映近代歷史上強勢文化與弱勢文化之間關係的普遍現象，便將結尾改成了：\r\n\r\nThe answer has been there since they tried to educate the locally foreign uncivilized boy.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n（中文版） \r\n\r\n還有多少土地要接受子彈的教誨和叮嚀\r\n\r\n還有多少生命會消失於戰機的咆嘯與雷鳴\r\n\r\n還有多少戰爭要贏才能讓他們真正擁有和平\r\n\r\n答案來自啊 有些人總試圖要別人也學會所謂文明\r\n\r\n\r\n倉庫字典：\r\n\r\nlocally foreign uncivilized boy　＂當地很外國的＂不文明男孩\r\n\r\n嗯，這首四行詩，是不是好像很賽德克巴萊了呢？\r\nBob Tone作曲，大國的演唱。\r\n\r\n歌曲中，詩人還加入了刻意改寫的美國兒歌＜印地安男孩＞\r\n\r\nOne little, two little, three little Indians.\r\nFour little, five little, six little Indians.\r\nSeven little, eight little, nine little Indians.\r\nTen little Indians annoyed.\r\n\r\nOne lightened, two lightened, three lightened aliens.\r\nFour lightened, five lightened, six lightened aliens.\r\nSeven lightened, eight lightened, nine lightened aliens.\r\nTen lightened aliens annoyed.\r\n\r\n倉庫字典：\r\nIndians annoyed　很不爽的印地安人\r\nlightened aliens annoyed　＂被教化得很不爽的＂外國人\r\n', '2012-06-08 00:00:00', 2012, 20, 0, 1, 'Still, How Many           詞  演唱 　大國Gordon Tseng （附美國兒歌＜Ten Little Indians＞)    作曲編曲　Bob Tone（編曲附美國兒歌＜Ten Little Indians＞）　　\r\n*\r\nHow many lands will get showers of bullets made of new alloy?\r\nHow many creatures would perish after the jetfighters’ cool ‘hoy’?\r\nHow many wars does a nation have to win to own real peaceful joy? \r\nThe answer has been there since they tried to educate the locally foreign uncivilized boy.\r\n*\r\nOne little, two little, three little Indians.\r\nFour little, five little, six little Indians.\r\nSeven little, eight little, nine little Indians.\r\nTen little Indians annoyed.\r\n*\r\nOne lightened, two lightened, three lightened aliens.\r\nFour lightened, five lightened, six lightened aliens.\r\nSeven lightened, eight lightened, nine lightened aliens.\r\nTen lightened aliens annoyed.\r\n*\r\nHow many lands?\r\nHow many creatures?\r\nHow many wars? \r\n*\r\n\r\n倉庫字典：\r\nIndians annoyed　很不爽的印地安人\r\nlightened aliens annoyed　＂被教化得很不爽的＂外國人\r\n\r\n\r\n', '', 361, '', 'Bob Tone（編曲附美國兒歌＜Ten Little Indians＞', '大國Gordon Tseng（附美國兒歌＜Ten Little Indians＞)  ', '四行倉庫', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-05-11 21:46:37', '2015-03-12 13:52:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
